<item>
            <title>[SOLR-3784] Schema-Browser hangs because of similarity</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3784</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Opening the Schema-Browser with the Default Configuration, switching the selection to type=int throws an error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;Uncaught TypeError: Cannot call method &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;esc&apos;&lt;/span&gt; of undefined &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// schema-browser.js:893&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On the first Look, this was introduced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3572&quot; title=&quot;Make Schema-Browser show custom similarities&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-3572&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-3572&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; .. right? &lt;/p&gt;</description>
